cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a deep learning framework for personalized recommendation, which involves learning non-linear relationships between users and items. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). However, since the focus of the paper is on developing a deep learning model for recommendation, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category.
